subproject.description: The porject will enable Kazakhstan to prepare and submit its Third National Communication to the Conference of Parties (CoP) of the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change in accordance with its commitments as a Party to the Convention as mandated by articles 4 and 12 of the Convention and subsequent CoP decisions.
subproject.title: UNFCCC 3d National Commun.
